    General Stores in Thane, Mumbai

    In India, general stores or mom-n-pop shops are generally referred to as 'kiranas'. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Depending on the location of the store  whether in a rural village or an urban metropolis  the stock keeping units or pack sizes of the packaged goods may differ. These store owners work in conjunction with wholesalers, distributors, and retailers forming a wide network in the city or town. Please scroll up to find a list of General Stores in Thane, Mumbai.
